**Input:**

```json
db.listingsAndReviews.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "geoWithin": {
        "path": "address.location",
        "box": {
          "bottomLeft": {
            "type": "Point",
            "coordinates": [112.467, -55.050]
          },
          "topRight": {
            "type": "Point",
            "coordinates": [168.000, -9.133]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 3
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "name": 1,
      "address": 1
    }
  }
])

```

